OL,3,CUnions warn Labour not to water down
OL,4,Cpackage on workers' rights
OL,6,FLabour is facing a union backlash over
OL,7,Freported plans to water down its
OL,8,Fpackage of workers' rights in the
OL,9,Fcoming weeks.
OL,11,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,12,Fwarned "a red line will be crossed" if
OL,13,Fthe party U-turns on previous
OL,14,Femployment pledges while TUC president
OL,15,FMatt Wrack said any weakening of
OL,16,Fpolicy will draw a "hostile reaction".
