OL,6,FLabour is set to announce all policies
OL,7,Fin its "new deal" for workers will go
OL,8,Fthrough a formal consultation process
OL,9,Fwith businesses, which could delay
OL,10,Ftheir implementation or see them toned
OL,11,Fdown, the Financial Times reported on
OL,12,FWednesday.
OL,14,FThe party originally promised to bring
OL,15,Fforward legislation within its first
OL,16,F100 days in government to enact the
OL,17,Freforms.
