OL,3,CUnions warn Labour not to water down
OL,4,Cpackage on workers' rights
OL,6,FThe report prompted a fierce response
OL,7,Ffrom union leaders, with Ms Graham
OL,8,Fsaying: "Choosing May Day to give
OL,9,Fnotice of watering down your promise
OL,10,Fto overhaul one of the worst sets of
OL,11,Femployment rights in Europe is beyond
OL,12,Firony.
OL,14,F"If Labour do not explicitly recommit
OL,15,Fto what they have already pledged,
OL,16,Fnamely that the New Deal for Workers
OL,17,Fwill be delivered in full within the
OL,18,Ffirst 100 days of office, then a red
OL,19,Fline will be crossed."
