OL,3,CUnions warn Labour not to water down
OL,4,Cpackage on workers' rights
OL,6,FMr Wrack told the FT: "My message is
OL,7,Fvery clear, no rolling back... if
OL,8,Fthere is any more rolling back on the
OL,9,FNew Deal, they can expect a hostile
OL,10,Freaction to it."
OL,12,FLabour will still promise workers
OL,13,Fbasic protections from day one of
OL,14,Femployment but companies will be able
OL,15,Fto impose probationary periods and
OL,16,Fstaff could be dismissed for "fair
OL,17,Freasons", according to the paper.
