OL,4,Cpackage on workers' rights
OL,6,FA party spokesperson said: "The New
OL,7,FDeal will be a core part of Labour's
OL,8,Foffer to the country and we will be
OL,9,Fcampaigning on this ahead of the
OL,10,Fgeneral election.
OL,12,F"Labour's New Deal for Working People
OL,13,Fwas agreed at the party's National
OL,14,FPolicy Forum last summer building upon
OL,15,Four Green Paper.
OL,17,F"Our commitments to bring forward
OL,18,Flegislation to Parliament within 100
OL,19,Fdays to deliver the New Deal and to
OL,20,Fconsult widely on implementation have
OL,21,Fnot changed."
