OL,6,FThe New Deal would be the latest
OL,7,FLabour policy to be scaled back after
OL,8,Fthe party diluted its flagship #28-
OL,9,Fbillion-a-year green spending pledge.
OL,11,FThe Opposition blamed the Government's
OL,12,Fhandling of the economy when it
OL,13,Fconfirmed the row-back in February,
OL,14,Fciting Liz Truss's mini-budget in
OL,15,FSeptember 2022 and higher interest
OL,16,Frates.
